    <h2 class="dek">White people win again at the Grammys.</h2>
    
    <div class="byline" id="main_byline">
        By <a rel="author" href="http://www.slate.com/authors.carl_wilson.html">Carl Wilson</a>
    </div>
    

    





  
  
  


